              "snippet": "Coffee is a globally popular, brewed beverage made from roasted coffee beans. It is celebrated for its rich flavor and stimulating effects, acting as a natural energy boost. Coffee is highly versatile, consumed steaming hot or chilled over ice, and can be customized with various types of milk and sweeteners.",
